EMPLOYEE HANDBOOK 2025
======================

LEAVE POLICY
============
Annual Leave: 20 days
Sick Leave: 10 days
Casual Leave: 5 days
Maternity Leave: 180 days
Paternity Leave: 15 days
Earned Leave (can be carried forward): 5 days max

WORK FROM HOME POLICY
====================
Remote Work Days: 2 days per week
Prerequisites: Minimum 6 months service
Approval: Manager approval required
Equipment Support: Company provides laptop
Internet Allowance: ₹1000 per month

SALARY REVIEW SCHEDULE
====================
Primary Review: March (Annual)
Mid-Year Review: September
Performance Bonus: Based on KPIs
Increment Range: 5-15%

BENEFITS
========
Health Insurance: Full coverage for employee + family
Dental Coverage: ₹25000 per annum
Vision Coverage: ₹10000 per annum
Life Insurance: 5x annual salary
Retirement Plan: Company match up to 12%

FLEXIBLE TIMING
===============
Standard Hours: 9 AM - 6 PM
Flexible Start: 8:30 AM - 10 AM
Flexible End: 5:30 PM - 7 PM

CODE OF CONDUCT
===============
- Maintain professional standards
- Confidentiality of company data
- Respect for colleagues
- Ethical business practices
- No discrimination or harassment

DISCIPLINARY PROCEDURES
=======================
1. Verbal Warning (First offense)
2. Written Warning (Second offense)
3. Suspension (Serious violations)
4. Termination (Repeated or grave violations)

For detailed information, please contact HR Department
